i v\'edi c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 \'ae\'b8nh v\'b5o thu nh\'cbp, 
\par \'a7\'b7 tho\'b6 thu\'cbn d\'ad\'edi \'ae\'a9y:
\par }{\b \'a7i\'d2u 1. 
\par }{Ph\'b9m vi \'b8p d\'f4ng:
\par Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y \'ae\'ad\'eec \'b8p d\'f4ng cho c\'b8c \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng l\'b5 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng c\'ad tr\'f3 c\'f1a m\'e9t ho\'c6c c\'b6 hai N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t.
\par }{\b \'a7i\'d2u 2.
\par }{C\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 bao g\'e5m trong Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh:
\par 1. Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y \'b8p d\'f4ng \'ae\'e8i v\'edi c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 do m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t ho\'c6c c\'b8c c\'ac quan ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n c\'ac s\'eb hay ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n \'ae\'dea ph\'ad\'acng c\'f1a N\'ad\'edc \'ae\'e3, \'ae\'b8
nh v\'b5o thu nh\'cbp b\'cat k\'d3 h\'d7nh th\'f8c \'b8p d\'f4ng c\'f1a c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 \'ae\'e3 nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o.
\par 2. T\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 thu tr\'aan t\'e6ng thu nh\'cbp, ho\'c6c nh\'f7ng ph\'c7n c\'f1a thu nh\'cbp bao g\'e5m c\'b8c kho\'b6n thu\'d5 \'ae\'e8i v\'edi l\'eei nhu\'cbn t\'f5 vi\'d6c chuy\'d3n nh\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'e9ng s\'b6n ho\'c6c b\'cat 
\'ae\'e9ng s\'b6n, c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 \'ae\'b8nh tr\'aan t\'e6ng s\'e8 ti\'d2n l\'ad\'acng ho\'c6c ti\'d2n c\'abng do x\'dd nghi\'d6p chi tr\'b6 \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'ad\'eec coi l\'b5 thu\'d5 \'ae\'b8nh v\'b5o thu nh\'cbp.
\par 3. Nh\'f7ng lo\'b9i thu\'d5 hi\'d6n h\'b5nh \'ae\'ad\'eec \'b8p d\'f4ng trong Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y l\'b5:
\par a. T\'b9i Vi\'d6t Nam:
\par (i) Thu\'d5 thu nh\'cbp c\'b8 nh\'a9n;
\par (ii) Thu\'d5 l\'eei t\'f8c; v\'b5
\par (iii) Thu\'d5 chuy\'d3n l\'eei nhu\'cbn ra n\'ad\'edc ngo\'b5i;
\par (D\'ad\'edi \'ae\'a9y \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'e4i l\'b5 \ldblquote thu\'d5 Vi\'d6t Nam\rdblquote );
\par b. T\'b9i In-\'ae\'ab-n\'aa-xi-a:
\par Thu\'d5 thu nh\'cbp \'b8p d\'f4ng theo Lu\'cbt thu\'d5 thu nh\'cbp n\'a8m 1984 (s\'f6a \'ae\'e6i Lu\'cbt s\'e8 7 n\'a8m 1983);
\par (D\'ad\'edi \'ae\'a9y \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'e4i l\'b5 \ldblquote thu\'d5 In-\'ae\'ab-n\'aa-xi-a\rdblquote );
\par 4. Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y c\'f2ng s\'cf \'ae\'ad\'eec \'b8p d\'f4ng cho c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 c\'e3 t\'ddnh ch\'cat t\'ad\'acng t\'f9 hay v\'d2 c\'a8n b\'b6n gi\'e8ng nh\'ad c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 tr\'aan ban h\'b5nh sau ng\'b5y k\'fd Hi\'d6p \'ae\'de
nh n\'b5y \'ae\'d3 b\'e6 sung, ho\'c6c thay th\'d5 c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 hi\'d6n h\'b5nh. C\'b8c nh\'b5 ch\'f8c tr\'b8ch c\'e3 th\'c8m quy\'d2n c\'f1a hai N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t s\'cf th\'abng b\'b8o cho nhau bi\'d5t nh\'f7ng thay \'ae\'e6i c\'ac b\'b6
n trong c\'b8c lu\'cbt thu\'d5 c\'f1a t\'f5ng N\'ad\'edc.
\par }{\b \'a7i\'d2u 3
\par }{C\'b8c \'ae\'denh ngh\'dca chung:
\par 1. Theo n\'e9i dung c\'f1a Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y, tr\'f5 tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep ng\'f7 c\'b6nh \'ae\'dfi h\'e1i c\'f1a s\'f9 gi\'b6i th\'ddch kh\'b8c:
\par a. T\'f5 \ldblquote Vi\'d6t Nam\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 n\'ad\'edc C\'e9ng h\'dfa x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca Vi\'d6t Nam; khi d\'efng cho ngh\'dca \'ae\'dea l\'fd, t\'f5 \'ae\'e3 bao g\'e5m to\'b5n b\'e9 l\'b7nh th\'e6 qu\'e8c gia Vi\'d6t Nam, k
\'d3 c\'b6 l\'b7nh h\'b6i Vi\'d6t Nam, v\'b5 m\'e4i v\'efng \'eb ngo\'b5i v\'b5 g\'ben li\'d2n v\'edi l\'b7nh h\'b6i Vi\'d6t Nam m\'b5 theo lu\'cbt ph\'b8p Vi\'d6t Nam v\'b5 ph\'ef h\'eep v\'edi lu\'cbt ph\'b8p qu\'e8c t\'d5; Vi\'d6t Nam c\'e3 quy\'d2n ch
\'f1 quy\'d2n \'ae\'e8i v\'edi vi\'d6c th\'a8m d\'df v\'b5 khai th\'b8c t\'b5i nguy\'aan thi\'aan nhi\'aan c\'f1a \'ae\'b8y bi\'d3n, l\'dfng \'ae\'cat d\'ad\'edi \'ae\'b8y bi\'d3n v\'b5 kh\'e8i n\'ad\'edc \'eb tr\'aan;
\par b. T\'f5 \ldblquote In-\'ae\'ab-n\'aa-xi-a\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 n\'ad\'edc C\'e9ng h\'dfa x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca In-\'ae\'ab-n\'aa-xi-a; \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'denh ngh\'dca trong c\'b8c lu\'cbt c\'f1a In-\'ae\'ab-n\'aa-xi-a  v\'b5 c\'b8c v
\'efng g\'ben li\'d2n v\'edi l\'b7nh th\'e6 In-\'ae\'ab-n\'aa-xi-a m\'b5 t\'b9i \'ae\'e3 C\'e9ng h\'dfa In-\'ae\'ab-n\'aa-xi-a c\'e3 ch\'f1 quy\'d2n hay quy\'d2n t\'b5i ph\'b8n ph\'ef h\'eep v\'edi quy \'ae\'denh c\'f1a C\'abng \'ad\'edc Li\'aan Hi\'d6
p Qu\'e8c v\'d2 Lu\'cbt bi\'d3n n\'a8m 1982;
\par c. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t\rdblquote  v\'b5 \ldblquote N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t kia\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 Vi\'d6t Nam hay In-\'ae\'ab-n\'aa-xi-a t\'efy theo ng\'f7 c\'b6nh \'ae\'dfi h\'e1i;
\par d. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng\rdblquote  bao g\'e5m c\'b8 nh\'a9n, c\'abng ty hay b\'cat k\'fa t\'e6 ch\'f8c nhi\'d2u \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng;
\par e. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote c\'abng ty\rdblquote  \'ae\'d3 ch\'d8 t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'abng ty ho\'c6c b\'cat k\'fa m\'e9t th\'f9c th\'d3 n\'b5o \'ae\'ad\'eec coi l\'b5 t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'abng ty d\'ad\'edi gi\'b8c \'ae\'e9 thu\'d5;
\par f. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote x\'dd nghi\'d6p c\'f1a N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t\rdblquote  v\'b5 \ldblquote x\'dd nghi\'d6p c\'f1a N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t kia\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 m\'e9t x\'dd nghi\'d6p \'ae\'ad\'eec \'aei\'d2u h\'b5nh b\'ebi \'ae
\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng c\'ad tr\'f3 c\'f1a m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t v\'b5 m\'e9t x\'dd nghi\'d6p \'ae\'ad\'eec \'aei\'d2u h\'b5nh b\'ebi \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng c\'ad tr\'f3 c\'f1a N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t kia;
\par g. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng mang qu\'e8c t\'dech c\'f1a m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca:
\par (i) B\'cat k\'fa c\'b8 nh\'a9n mang qu\'e8c t\'dech c\'f1a m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t; hay
\par (ii) B\'cat k\'fa ph\'b8p nh\'a9n, t\'e6 ch\'f8c h\'efn v\'e8n v\'b5 hi\'d6p h\'e9i n\'b5o c\'e3 t\'ad c\'b8ch \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'cap nh\'cbn theo c\'b8c lu\'cbt c\'e3 hi\'d6u l\'f9c t\'b9i m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t;
